atically created by MailPoet with all of your WooCommerce customers. It also includes “Guest" customers. If WooCommerce is active, users that installed or updated the plugin should have chosen if they wanted to add the customers as “Subscribed” or “Unsubscribed” to the WooCommerce Customers list.'=>'The WooCommerce Customers list is a list automatically created by MailPoet with all of your WooCommerce customers. It also includes “Guest" customers. If WooCommerce is active, users that installed or updated the plugin should have chosen if they wanted to add the customers as “Subscribed” or “Unsubscribed” to the WooCommerce Customers list.','The automation follows a different path based on specified conditions.'=>'自動化は、指定された条件に基づいて異なるパスに従います。','The automation has been saved.'=>'自動化が保存されました。','The automation would go through the yes flow if <operator>all of</operator> the following conditions are met:'=>'次の条件が<operator>すべて</operator>満たされる場合、自動化は 「はい」フローを実行します。','The automation would go through the yes flow if <operator>any of</operator> the following conditions are met:'=>'次の条件の<operator>いずれか</operator>が満たされる場合、自動化は 「はい」フローを実行します。','The automation would go through the yes flow if the following conditions are met:'=>'次の条件が満たされる場合、自動化は「はい」フローを実行します。','The automation would only be started if <operator>all of</operator> the following trigger conditions are met:'=>'自動化は、次のトリガー条件が<operator>すべて</operator>満たされた場合にのみ開始されます。','The automation would only be started if <operator>any of</operator> the following trigger conditions are met:'=>'自動化は、次のトリガー条件の<operator>いずれか</operator>が満たされた場合にのみ開始されます。','The automation would only be started if the following trigger conditions are met:'=>'自動化は、次のトリガー条件が満たされた場合にのみ開始されます。','The beginner’s guide to segmentation'=>'セグメンテーションの初心者向けガイド','The changes you made may not be saved'=>'変更は保存されない場合があります。','The characters entered do not match with the previous CAPTCHA.'=>'入力した文字が以前の CAPTCHA と一致しません。','The characters you entered did not match the CAPTCHA 